# Web App

Minimal Vite + React application that consumes shared components from `packages/ui`.

## Development

From the repository root:

```bash
<%= runCommand%> dev
```

Or run only this app (build `ui` first if needed):

```bash
<%= runCommand%> build --filter=<%= scope%>ui
<%= runCommand%> dev --filter=<%= scope%>web
```
